snippet.title: Final Fantasy Type-0 HD -- Enter the Fray Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
SQUARE ENIX today premiered a new trailer to celebrate the opening day of Paris Games Week. This latest trailer, “Enter the Fray” transports viewers to the dynamic and enthralling world of Orience, where a turbulent war of nations threatens to tear the land apart.

http://www.finalfantasytype0.com
